<script type="text/javascript">
    $(window).ready(function () {
        // 가입하기 완료
        $('.confirm_btn.completed .btn_g').click(function () {
            location.href = "/Account/login";
        });
    });
</script>

<article id="mainContent" class="content-article">
    <div class="cont_sign">
        <strong class="blind">가입하기 완료</strong>
        <h2 class="tit_m">
            환영합니다!
        </h2>
        <div class="tit_s">
            <span>계정 가입이 완료되었습니다.</span>
            <span>계정 하나로 다양한 서비스를 편리하게 이용해보세요!</span>
        </div>
        <form class="sign-completed">
            <div class="frm-body">
                <div class="profile-info">
                    <img src="~/Resource/Images/Common/userProfile.jpg" />
                    <span>@ViewBag.Email</span>
                    <span class="user-name">@ViewBag.Name</span>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="confirm_btn completed">
                <button type="button" class="btn_g">시작하기</button>
            </div>
        </form>
    </div>
</article>